args: You want me to find your missing wife?\nTell me what happened.
One day she just up and vanished on me.\nShe's always been a mite sickly, and I\nworry she may have collapsed somewhere.
The power of my ninja bride skills\nwill have her found in no time!
...Or so I thought, but this isn't going very\nwell at ALL. Looks like I'll need to bring\nin the big firepower for this one.
Ooo, I heard a JUICY rumor the other day!\nThe wife of the man across the way has\nfinally had enough and wants a DIVORCE!
Heavens, really? Oh, but HERE'S a story:\nApparently an old lady has gone missing!
That's the first I've heard of that.\nBut never mind old peopleâ€”let me\ntell you about that new girl in town!
...So in the end, I heard loads of useless\ngossip, and nothing at all about the old\nwoman I'm interested in. Yaaay, me!
Wait, I shouldn't be celebrating that.\nWhat the heck am I going to DO?
What is it? Did you find something?
Wait... Is that who I think it is?!
My, but that is a lovely dress,\nyoung lady.
Hey, thanks. It's a style of wedding dress\nfrom Hinomoto. Super pretty, right?!
A wedding dress? Oh, how lovely.\nThat certainly takes me back.
What I wouldn't give to return to those\nhalcyon days of yore...
But alas, I'm just a wrinkled old lady now.\nNothing at all like the pretty young thing\nthat he first fell in love with.
Why, my beloved, of course! He's so very\nkind, and we've been there for each other\nthrough thick and thin across the years.
But lately, I only seem to make life harder\nfor him. I seem to be past my sell-by date.
So one day, I ran off. I simply couldn't\nbear to be a burden on him any longer.
I'm sure he doesn't feel that way. In fact,\nI know he's super worried about you!

And yet I just can't stand the thought
of returning to him as I am now.
Not unless there were some way
to be pretty again...
If it's facing him you're worried about,\nmy ninja bride skills will give you the\nconfidence boost you need!
Surely you aren't implying that you can\nreturn me to my younger self, because\nsuch a thing is simply not possible.
Ha! Being a ninja bride is all ABOUT\nmaking the impossible possible!
Besides, what better way to show the\npower of ninja bride skills than by\nhelping two lovers reunite?
So you just leave this to me!
...Sorry for the wait, but I've brought\nsomeone here to see you.
Is it my wife?! Is she all right?!
Oh, she's BETTER than all right! Look!
Heavens! You look just like you did\nwhen we first met! ...Is this a trick?
No tricks! She really IS your wife!
This is the power of bridal transformation!\nIt can reach into days long gone and bring\nyour former self to the present!
After I told this young lady here how I\ncouldn't bear to face you as I was,\nshe used magic to make me look young.
Even though it will only last a short while,\nyou can at least see the woman you once\nfell in love with again.
I'm sorry for all the trouble I've been\ncausing you. But just look how pretty I\nam now! There's not a wrinkle to be seen!
Wait, is THAT what has been troubling\nyou this entire time? What nonsense!
I'm just as wrinkled as you, aren't I?
Our wrinkles serve as proof of the full\nlives we've led together. The more you\nhave, the more memories you've made!
Well, that took a turn for the adorable.
Thank you so much for finding my wife,\nyoung lady. And that ninja transformation\nwas quite a sight, too!
Uh...sure? I mean, um, you're welcome.
I owe you my deepest thanks, young lady;\nyou helped me to remember what is\nTRULY important.
*sniff* Aw, you guys are the best.\nStay happy together, all right?
Score one more for ninja bride skills!\n...Although I suppose I can't actually\ntake much of the credit this time.
It was so moving to see the love\nbetween a real married couple!
I've got my work cut out as a ninja bride\nif I want to compare to that.
But I'm gonna do my best, guys!
